{
  "page": "Little Lord Lazyeye",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Little Lord Lazyeye</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nLittle Lord Lazyeye</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\nbefore <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_273_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">273&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Little Lord Lazyeye</b> was the nickname Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> gave to an unidentified suitor of his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia Martell</a> during the trip the siblings took in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_273_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">273&#160;AC</a>, during which their <a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">mother</a> hoped to <a href=\"/index.php/Betrothal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Betrothal\">betroth</a> either one of them, or both.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">Martells</a> stopped at <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Arbor\" title=\"Arbor\">Arbor</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Shield_Islands\" title=\"Shield Islands\">Shield Islands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Crakehall\" title=\"Crakehall\">Crakehall</a> before arriving to <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Little Lord Lazeye was either a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">Dayne</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\">Redwyne</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">Hightower</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Grimm\" title=\"House Grimm\">Grimm</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Chester\" title=\"House Chester\">Chester</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hewett\" title=\"House Hewett\">Hewett</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Serry\" title=\"House Serry\">Serry</a> or a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Crakehall\" title=\"House Crakehall\">Crakehall</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Lord_Lazyeye&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/